        "TileImage": "$($repository ab22f88d-f567-43a2-b20f-0ecc17257ffe).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47, and welcome to France, Paris. I have now managed to log in Helmut Kruger, who has been talked about for ages. Many clients have sent us requests to take care of him. Helmut is known to be beloved and charismatic by his fans, when in truth his popularity and fan base are only based on the fact that he cannot have enemies. When someone tries to compete against Helmut, he sends someone to sabotage their show. The client wants to murder him for a better future. Good hunting 47.",
